msd.user.inf

Class UserQuery

  • java.lang.Object
    • msd.user.inf.UserQuery
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    InputCapture
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AuthorQuery

    public class UserQuery
extends java.lang.Object
implements InputCapture
    Class that is used to set the user query supplied by the input This class's object is visible to the Query Engine which extracts the user supplied inputs to run the corresponding query.
